getting to know me better.

171
00:18:04,983 --> 00:18:09,443
Have you noticed I'm as
nervous as an Olympic athlete?.

172
00:18:09,655 --> 00:18:13,921
Sure. And I've been wondering why.

173
00:18:16,028 --> 00:18:21,834
