01:27:23,438 --> 01:27:24,166
Yeah.

481
01:27:26,407 --> 01:27:27,874
We don't have
the utensils, anyway.

482
01:27:28,576 --> 01:27:31,602
I think we should keep moving.

483
01:27:32,981 --> 01:27:36,314
When it gets cooler,
I'm heading south.

484
01:27:37,352 --> 01:27:40,121
Still hoping to find Annie?.

485
01:27:40,121 --> 01:27:42,521
We have to
wait for the ship anyway.

486
01:27:44,092 --> 01:27:46,560
Shouldn't we set up a defense?.

487
01:27:47,929 --> 01:27:52,300
I just can't figure out
who that mystery man is,

488
01:27:52,300 --> 01:27:54,802
if he exists.

489
01:27:54,802 --> 01:28:01,799
The captain is right. I agree with
him. We have to try to stay alive.

490
01:28:02,243 --> 01:28:05,735
Yeah, we're not gonna just
sit here and wait to be killed.

491
01:28:06,714 --> 01:28:10,151
Lemuan, there's some
whiskey left. W ant a drink?.

492
01:28:10,151 --> 01:28:11,812
No, thank you.
You know I don't drink.

493
01:28:18,293 --> 01:28:22,497
My God, what a barbaric situation!
Look what's become of us.

494
01:28:22,497 --> 01:28:26,263
We're like wild
animals trying to survive.

495
01:28:27,602 --> 01:28:31,506
You're losing
your dignity too, eh?.

496
01:28:31,506 --> 01:28:34,175
I suppose that's
easy for you to do.

497
01:28:34,175 --> 01:28:36,541
Depends on the
circumstances, Lemuan.

498
01:28:43,184 --> 01:28:44,886
Find any good ones?.

499
01:28:44,886 --> 01:28:46,751
Up to now,
I've just destroyed my hands.

500
01:28:47,855 --> 01:28:49,948
Want some?.

501
01:28:50,358 --> 01:28:52,986
I'm sweating already.

502
01:28:53,561 --> 01:28:54,858
Your loss.....

503
01:28:56,631 --> 01:28:58,360
Be careful,
you could get drunk.

504
01:28:59,667 --> 01:29:02,537
Afraid I'll
lose my respect for you?.

505
01:29:02,537 --> 01:29:08,276
Afraid I'll
lose my respect for you?.

506
01:29:08,276 --> 01:29:09,766
Wait, I'll take care of it.

507
01:29:15,083 --> 01:29:17,551
Hey,
where'd you learn to do that?.

508
01:29:19,787 --> 01:29:21,846
Where do you think?.

509
01:29:22,824 --> 01:29:24,689
Sorry I asked.

510
01:29:27,462 --> 01:29:28,986
Come on. Fuck me?.

511
01:29:29,864 --> 01:29:31,161
No, thank you.

512
01:29:32,867 --> 01:29:35,097
Why, you afraid?.

513
01:29:37,171 --> 01:29:38,900
Drink and you'll feel better.

514
01:29:39,807 --> 01:29:45,513
Wouldn't you like to fuck a countess?.
It might be your last chance.

515
01:29:45,513 --> 01:29:49,950
Tomorrow we might all be dead...
dead! Understand?.

516
01:34:16,384 --> 01:34:20,021
Benoit!! Now I understand.
That was your boat I found.

517
01:34:20,021 --> 01:34:21,989
Who did this to you?.

518
01:34:21,989 --> 01:34:26,827
A cross between monster and a
man. He was dressed in rags.

519
01:34:26,827 --> 01:34:29,230
C'mon, I'll take you to our camp.

520
01:34:29,230 --> 01:34:30,356
No, Captain.

521
01:34:32,667 --> 01:34:37,161
That bastard broke
every bone in my body.

522
01:34:39,173 --> 01:34:44,304
Let me die in peace.
You'd better go rescue the woman.

523
01:34:44,745 --> 01:34:47,114
Woman?.
What woman are you talking about?.

524
01:34:47,114 --> 01:34:51,483
The dark-skinned girl.
She was a member of the expedition.

525
01:34:52,086 --> 01:34:53,576
Where is she?.?.

526
01:34:53,654 --> 01:35:01,356
Up there, in a cave. Listen to me,
Captain. Don't go up there alone!!

527
01:40:46,607 --> 01:40:48,175
Where is it?.

528
01:40:48,175 --> 01:40:49,233
I don't know.

529
01:40:50,044 --> 01:40:51,602
We'd better hurry.

530
01:40:58,252 --> 01:40:59,241
Let's go.

531
01:41:32,986 --> 01:41:34,112
Get behind me!

532
01:42:31,845 --> 01:42:33,437
No, Demaduro, no!!

533
01:42:42,856 --> 01:42:43,515
Let's go!

534
01:47:34,314 --> 01:47:37,451
We're out of gas, water and food.

535
01:47:37,451 --> 01:47:40,215
I'm afraid the current
is taking us to God knows where

536
01:47:40,287 --> 01:47:43,120
far from the shipping lanes.

537
01:47:43,790 --> 01:47:48,056
It's so unfair. We escape from that
monster, only to end up like this.

538
01:47:49,429 --> 01:47:51,465
You know what
you do in a case like this?.

539
01:47:51,465 --> 01:47:53,695
Just make believe
that everything is OK.

540
01:47:54,367 --> 01:47:55,527
Oh, really?.

541
01:47:55,769 --> 01:47:59,940
Sure, my love. How would you
like a nice continental breakfast?.

542
01:47:59,940 --> 01:48:03,103
Scrambled eggs with
2 big slices of bacon.

543
01:48:03,810 --> 01:48:08,076
You're so silly. God, what l
wouldn't give for a meal like that!

544
01:48:09,082 --> 01:48:12,074
Then God bless
the captain of that ship.

545
01:48:14,221 --> 01:48:16,689
Hey! We're over here!!

546
01:48:17,424 --> 01:48:20,291
-We're here!
-Help us!!

547
01:48:21,261 --> 01:48:23,889
Over here! Help us!

